      "questionHtml": "Given a metric space \\((X,d)\\), write the definition of its Borel \\(\\sigma\\)-algebra \\(\\mathcal B(X)\\). Provide classes of Borel sets and characterize \\(\\mathcal B(\\mathbb R)\\), \\(\\mathcal B(\\mathbb R^N)\\).",
